{"tid":2167280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"73名美國共和黨兼前國安部成員倒戈支持 China Joe !","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T06:49:10.000Z","uid":118346,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"47419033ec7304a2c7fd8204a3f12d7718fddf87","tid":2167280,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"73名美國共和黨兼前國安部成員倒戈，於昨日公開宣布支持民主黨總統候選人拜登角逐總統，令倒戈相向的共和黨人勢力愈來愈大。他們發表的聲明更指責總統特朗普「貪腐」和「不適合擔任總統職位」。<br />\n<br />\n他們又指特朗普的所作作為令他愈來愈靠攏如金正恩、普京等獨裁者的行為，批評他破壞法治，無力帶領美國走出疫情困局，更嚴重打擊美國作為「世界領袖」的地位。他們表示雖然他們的政策理念未必與拜登一致，但相信拜登有能力重建「總統的尊嚴」及「美國的世界領導地位」。<br />\n<br />\n這批公開倒戈的國安部人員，全都曾與前總統列根、布殊父子及特朗普共事，包括前CIA局長Michael Hayden、前CIA及FBI局長William Webster及前國家情報總監Michael Leiter等首長級官員。近來很多高職級和地位的共和黨人及特朗普前支持者都公開反對特朗普角逐連任，前俄亥俄州州長John Kasich曾參與民主黨總統造大會，前白宮通訊聯絡主任Anthony Scaramucci更稱特朗普「瘋狂」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死奶共民主黨左膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4189e1165668bcb22567c177328f39b51176137","tid":2167280,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8292702c9d1b419a5dc993bbdcb0f6b58cc8f2d5","tid":2167280,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ndeed state<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/f